title: Wordfinder 8 Pro Multilang ISO-ABSOKT
description:
WordFinder 8 Professional &auml;r s&ouml;kmotorn som hanterar de elektroniska 
ordb&ouml;ckerna - sl&aring;r upp ordet, ger dig &ouml;vers&auml;ttningarna samt klistrar 
in ordet i din applikation. Som att ha en bokhylla i din dator, helt enkelt.

Som en bonus finns p&aring; cd:n ocks&aring; Wordfinder Language suite och 
Wordfinder Skribent, l&auml;s mer om dom p&aring; websidan.

Using dictionaries with WordFinder requires the WordFinder 8 Professional 
search tool. WordFinder 8 Professional is a search tool for electronic 
dictionaries ? It finds the required headword, retrieves and pastes 
translations into your document. 

This is a multilanguage release, the search engine can be installed
 with the following languages:
 Danish
 Dutch
 English
 Finnish
 German
 Norwegian
 Spanish
 Swedish
 
 It is also possible to change language on-the-fly from the menu, 
 after install.   

          Installation:                                                    
    Packa upp, br&auml;nn eller mounta, installera och anv&auml;nd keygen i 
    /crack-katalogen f&ouml;r att generera samtliga koder som beh&ouml;vs. 
    CD:n inneh&aring;ller 111 olika ordb&ouml;cker:-)......
    
    Unpack and burn or mount the image file. Install and use the keygen in 
    the /crack dir to generate all the neccessary codes. This release 
    contains 111 different dictionaries:-)....
